{"tid":1943110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"第二批湖北回港包機　乘客不獲發保護衣　回港後可自行解散","createTime":"2020-03-25T12:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T13:20:05.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"09b41521e4ee72432eaaf9833f0c3350bbb288db","tid":1943110,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>第二批湖北回港包機 乘客不獲發保護衣 回港後可自行解散</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n政府今日（25日）派出第二批包機接滯留湖北的港人回港。曾先生一家三口今早11時由天門市出發，乘坐政府安排的私家車，最終花近3小時，於下午2時才抵達武漢機場。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，由高速公路進入武漢市時要出示通行證件，但不用量體溫，他們到達機場才有港府人員為他們量體溫，一家三人體溫正常。另外，曾先生說，包機乘客每人獲贈一個「福袋」，內有消毒紙巾及口罩，但未有獲發保護衣。包機上不能飲食，有別於上次包機乘客獲發杯麵、水果等小食，曾先生稱僅獲發一條能量條。<br />\n<br />\n曾先生一家將會乘搭晚上7時的包機回港；抵港後將自行解散，回家接受14日家居檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200325/s00001/1585122330180/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%B9%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E5%8C%85%E6%A9%9F-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E8%A1%A3-%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E8%A7%A3%E6%95%A3?fbclid=IwAR2hGi1JILiQ-i-VrMAzNgRmV02wlaLlLxqVadsaiOtPdDQk6qI8zTlg8Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200325%2Fs00001%2F1585122330180%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25A1%25A3-%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2595%25A3%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2hGi1JILiQ-i-VrMAzNgRmV02wlaLlLxqVadsaiOtPdDQk6qI8zTlg8Zw&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4fUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=ea522f3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200325%2Fs0